# Key Business Insights

The project identified several important business insights:

- Customers with month-to-month contracts are more likely to churn.
- Customers with higher monthly charges have a greater probability of leaving.
- Long-term contract customers demonstrate significantly lower churn rates.
- Electronic Check is one of the most common payment methods among churned customers.
- Customer tenure is one of the strongest indicators of churn.
- Customers with higher predicted Lifetime Value should be prioritised for retention campaigns.

